AUthorize after fulfilling order. If unfulfiled then order cannot proceed.
Authorization reference ID required
Action Capture payment amount
Capture reference
Capture Note payment received
Confirm order with Amazon ref ID

GetOrderReferenceDetails operation to get the remaining buyer information like name and shipping address. 
Before an order reference is confirmed, only the City, StateOrRegion, PostalCode, and CountryCode elements are returned in the call to GetOrderReferenceDetails.



POST /OffAmazonPayments/2013-01-01 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: x-www-form-urlencoded
Host: mws.amazonservices.com
User-Agent: <Your User Agent Header>

   
